description: K2A Knaust & Andersson Fastigheter AB (publ) is a SE-based company operating in Real Estate Management & Development industry. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 133 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2015-04-02. K2A Knaust & Andersson Fastigheter publ AB is a Sweden-based real estate company. The company is engaged in long-term management of own rental units, primarily comprising various types of accommodation. The company develops and offers modern, functional houses as well as community buildings and other commercial properties. Its operations are concentrated in Malardalen and university and college towns. The firm builds a portfolio of approximately 1,500 rental units, majority of which is student housing. The company is also engaged in construction activities, primarily using wood in order to ensure insulation and sustainability and due to its renewable features.
